These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, german, brazilian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the german##1
2. the american is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | french | brazilian | german |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, snowboarding, water-polo
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | climbing  | surfing  | water-polo |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
House: tower, modern, cape-cod, palace
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the palace house is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the modern house##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the modern house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| House          | palace | cape-cod | modern    | tower      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ebony, lilac, yellow
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes yellow##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Color   | lilac       | aquamarine   | ebony    | yellow  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, bellflower, dahlia, daffodil
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Flower   | bellflower  | tulip    | dahlia   | daffodil       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

