.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, brown, turquise, black
1. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who likes black is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Color     | black | turquise  | apricot     | brown |

