.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, pakistani, chinese, nigerian
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the indian is between the pakistani and the person eating pepper##2
4. the indian is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Nationality    | nigerian     | pakistani | indian     | chinese  |

