.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, canasta, backgammon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, backgammon-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is backgammon-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is backgammon-polo is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Game   | whist   | backgammon   | bridge      | canasta      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | backgammon-polo | biathlon |

