4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fisherman is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | satire | thriller  |
| Job     | firefighter   | writer  | software-developer  | fisherman |

