.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, modern, gothic-revival
1. the modern house is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the modern house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

