.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, soccer, lacrosse
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | soccer | snowboarding | sailing    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

