.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, azure, mauve, black
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who likes green and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who likes black##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Color         | green | mauve   | black | azure |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 